general
	keep knees soft
	step on balls of feet, not toes (centre of balance of arch)
	be more grounded by moving like a cat - knead the floor with feet
	breathe to 

basic
	keep feet on floor to make soft footfalls
	right hand - up to armpit, then fold in

lateral
	keep level

return
	arc motion to guide momentum back during rebound
	lunge - keep knees bent and weight stacked (core over hips over knees over feet)
	follow forward during catch

bonus
	keep line of travel for follow open as extra info

yoyo
	redirect by moving with legs and core, not arms